---
title: Grilled Cheese Sandwich Bar One recipe—endless ways to enjoy!
description: How do you make everyone happy at dinnertime? A DIY grilled cheese sandwich bar! Keep it simple with melty cheddar and tomato, or, go all out with garlic mushrooms, jammy onion, and a honey Dijon spread (plus roasted potato wedges on the side). Everyone at the table will say cheese!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/669560dfb0a47382be870343-93306ca6.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/669560dfb0a47382be870343-en-US.pdf
nutrition:
  calories: 950 kcal
  fat: 61 g
  saturated fat: 26 g
  carbohydrates: 84 g
  sugar: 15 g
  protein: 28 g
  fiber: 5 g
  sodium: 1040 mg
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/grilled-cheese-sandwich-bar-669560dfb0a47382be870343
course: main course
